Toys R Us Attack of the Killer Demos!
name: Toys R Us: Attack of the Killer Demos!
overview: Toys R Us: Attack of the Killer Demos! is a PlayStation demo disc that contains demos of the games Contender, Legend of Legaia, R4: Ridge Racer Type 4, Xena: Warrior Princess, Cool Boarders 3, Ehrgeiz, and Elmo's Letter Adventure.
